snippet.title: HANGRY    Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2601510/HANGRY/

See what we are cooking up......

Play as Hangry, a beastly mercenary with an insatiable hunger hunting down fearsome monsters in a snack n' slash RPG. 

Traverse through barbequed woodlands and candy-coated caverns to find ingredients for Goutra, the chief chef of an alien underworld diner. 

Your goal is to find the finest cuts for Goutra and climb the ladder of the city's underbelly to become the planet's best hunter. 

But beware, you must resist the temptation to eat the merchandise.
